@startuml
title AutoLabeling（选择模型→推理→回填标注）时序
autonumber
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

actor User
participant "LabelingWidget" as LWidget
participant "AutoLabelingWidget" as ALW
participant "ModelManager" as MM
participant "QThread" as Thr
participant "GenericWorker" as Worker
participant "LoadedModel(model)" as Model
participant "Canvas/LabelList" as UI

== 选择模型 ==
User -> ALW: 从下拉框选择模型
ALW -> ALW: emit new_model_selected(model_name)
ALW -> MM: load_model(model_name)\n(内部可能下载/初始化/切线程)
MM --> ALW: new_model_status("Model loaded...")/model_loaded(model_config)
ALW -> ALW: update_visible_widgets(); on_new_model_loaded()

== 运行推理 ==
User -> ALW: 点击 Run（或快捷键 I）
ALW -> MM: predict_shapes_threading(image, filename,\ntext_prompt?, existing_shapes?)
MM -> MM: emit prediction_started
MM -> Thr: 创建 model_execution_thread
MM -> Worker: GenericWorker(predict_shapes, ...)
MM -> Worker: moveToThread(thread)
Thr -> Worker: started -> run()

Worker -> MM: predict_shapes(...)
MM -> Model: model.predict_shapes(...)
Model --> MM: AutoLabelingResult(shapes, replace, description, ...)
MM -> MM: emit new_auto_labeling_result(result)
MM -> MM: emit prediction_finished

MM -> ALW: (lambda) parent.new_shapes_from_auto_labeling(result)
ALW -> LWidget: new_shapes_from_auto_labeling(result)
LWidget -> UI: load_shapes()/更新列表/设置description\nset_dirty()

@enduml